Package: MADVAR
Type: Package
Title: Variance-Based Feature Selection in Biological data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person( 
      "Gilad", "Silberberg", 
      email = "gsilberberg@championsoncology.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Calculates a cutoff based on data variance. Also provides an exploration mode, where the variance density overlaid by the calculated cutoff is plotted.
Imports: 
    stats,
    modeest,
    ggplot2,
    assertthat
